                "description": "The line number is omitted",
                "name": "file"
              },
              {
                "description": "The lines are suppressed (same as --no-location)",
                "name": "never"
              }
            ]
          },
          "description": "[{full,file,never}] Controls '#: filename:line' lines. If the option is 'full' (the default if not given), the lines include both file name and line number. If it's 'file', the line number is omitted. If it's 'never', the lines are suppressed (same as --no-location). --add-location requires gettext 0.19 or newer",
